I"‹<h2 id="a-simple-jekyll-blog-theme">A simple Jekyll blog theme</h2>

<ul>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Resposive layout</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Preprocessor SASS</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Syntax highlight</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Author config</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Pagination</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Search bar</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Comments with Disqus</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Share posts</li>
  <li>:heavy_check_mark: Sitemap and seo tags</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h3 id="get-started-in-4-easy-steps">Get Started in 4 easy steps</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Download or clone repository <code>git clone https://github.com/mateussmedeiros/blade-theme.git</code></li>
  <li>Enter the folder: <code>cd blade-theme</code></li>
  <li>Install Ruby gems: <code>bundle install</code></li>
  <li>Start Jekyll server: <code>jekyll serve</code></li>
</ol>

<p>Access: <a href="http://localhost:4000">localhost:4000</a></p>

